ASTROLOGER REGISTRATION PROFILE FIELDS:
-------------------------------------
1. full_name
   - Type: String / Text
   - Description: The displayed public name of the astrologer.
   - Example: "Acharya Ramanand Shastri"
   - Required: Yes

2. spiritual_title
   - Type: String / Text
   - Description: A headline summarizing their expertise or lineage.
   - Example: "Vedic Hora & Vastu Authority"
   - Required: Yes

3. bio
   - Type: String / Text
   - Description: Detailed description of their methodology, ancestry, remedies, and background.
   - Example: "Over 16 years of experience reading charts under classical systems..."
   - Required: No (Recommended)

4. profile_photo
   - Type: String / URL
   - Description: A direct HTTPS URL link to the profile picture.
   - Example: "https://example.com/photos/shastri.jpg"
   - Required: No (Falls back to placeholder)

5. experience_years
   - Type: Integer
   - Description: Number of years active in offering consultations.
   - Example: 16
   - Required: Yes (Default: 5)

6. readings_count
   - Type: Integer
   - Description: Total consults or chart readings completed.
   - Example: 3500
   - Required: Yes (Default: 100)

7. charge_per_min
   - Type: Integer
   - Description: Coin consultation rate per minute.
   - Example: 60
   - Required: Yes (Default: 30)

8. languages
   - Type: Array of Strings / Text[]
   - Description: Languages spoken and understood during sessions.
   - Example: ["Hindi", "English", "Sanskrit"]
   - Required: Yes (At least 1)

9. specialties
   - Type: Array of Strings / Text[]
   - Description: Specialized areas of astrology.
   - Example: ["Kundli Milan", "Gemstone Advice", "Vastu Dosha", "KP Astrology"]
   - Required: Yes (At least 1)

10. city
    - Type: String / Text
    - Description: City of residence.
    - Example: "Varanasi"
    - Required: No

11. state
    - Type: String / Text
    - Description: State of residence.
    - Example: "Uttar Pradesh"
    - Required: No

12. is_online
    - Type: Boolean
    - Description: Real-time availability status indicator.
    - Example: true
    - Required: Yes (Default: true)
